62.9	Ishmael	Ishmael	Ishmael is a figure in the Hebrew Bible and the Qur'an, and was Abraham's first son according to Jews, Christians and Muslims. Ishmael was born of Abraham's marriage to Sarah's handmaiden Hagar (Genesis 16:3). According to the Genesis account, he died at the age of 137 (Genesis 25:17).	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/5a/Navez_Agar_et_Isma%C3%ABl.jpg/250px-Navez_Agar_et_Isma%C3%ABl.jpg
